  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Install required fonts: Chakra Petch, IBM Plex Sans, JetBrains Mono via Google Fonts.",
    "Implement the boot loader using pure CSS animations or Framer Motion/GSAP before showing the main R3F canvas.",
    "The main navigation MUST be a radial circular menu replacing the traditional header nav.",
    "Use react-three-fiber and @react-three/drei for the Neural Network Constellation background.",
    "Use shadcn/ui components for the Careers form but heavily customize them to remove borders and apply glassmorphism.",
    "Wrap sections and key panels in 'code-as-content' style text blocks using JetBrains Mono text-xs text-blue-500.",
    "Integrate Web Audio API for hover/click/boot sound effects as specified.",
    "Strictly adhere to the Blue/Black/White color palette. No purple, violet, or cyan.",
    "All interactive elements MUST have data-testid attributes.",
    "Ensure the JSON file path `/app/design_guidelines.json` is handed off."
  ]
}